American express - 15 digit
starts with 34 or 37

MasterCard - 16 digit
starts with 51 52 53 54 55

Visa - 13 or 16 digit
starts with 4

Card is valid if:
Sum of every other digit, starting from second last, multiplied by 2
Plus sum of every remaining digit / every other digit starting from the end
SUM has to be a multiple of 10

